                        </div>
                        <div class="download-info">
                            <h3>Half-Yearly Exam Schedule</h3>
                            <div class="download-meta">
                                <span><i class="ph-bold ph-hard-drives"></i> 600 KB</span>
                                <span><i class="ph-bold ph-calendar-blank"></i> Jul 2026</span>
